                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9758" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1466</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">881 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">以文化为翼，打造游戏营销新典范——《黑神话：悟空》开创中国游戏“天命之路”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Using Culture as Wings, Creating a New Paradigm of Game Marketing - ‘Black Myth: Wu kong’ Creates the ‘Path of Destiny’ for Chinese Games</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">唐文秀，吴海棠，王尚怡，毛雨薇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳市游科互动科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《黑神话：悟空》；文化IP策略；文化IP跨界营销；跨文化传播</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Black Myth: WuKong; Cultural IP Strategy; Cultural IP Cross-border Marketing Strategy; Cross-cultural communication</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在数字网络技术蓬勃发展的背景下，数字游戏成为中华优秀传统文化的现代化转型载体，以及我国文化“出海”的重要渠道之一。《黑神话：悟空》作为国内首款3A游戏大作，打破了长期以来欧美国家3A游戏的“垄断”，为中华文化走向世界开辟了新路径。本案例以《黑神话：悟空》为例，描述了《黑神话：悟空》团队在面对激烈竞争以及新媒体快速发展的市场环境下，以传统文化为基点，采取文化IP策略、文化原型理论以及跨文化传播策略的故事。通过对本案例的思考和学习，学生可以掌握文化原型理论、文化IP跨界营销策略以及跨文化传播策略的相关理论知识，并思考国产主机游戏的文化赋能措施，为其他国产主机游戏如何借助传统文化打造全球热度提供一定的参考价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the context of the vigorous development of digital network technology, digital games have become the carrier of the modernization and transformation of China&#39;s excellent traditional culture, as well as one of the important channels for China&#39;s culture to &quot;go overseas&quot;. As the first 3A game masterpiece in China, &quot;Black Myth: Wukong&quot; broke the long-term &quot;monopoly&quot; of 3A games in Europe and the United States, and opened up a new path for Chinese culture to go global. This case takes Black Myth: Wukong as an example to describe the story of the Black Myth: Wukong team, which takes traditional culture as the base and adopts cultural IP strategy, cultural archetype theory and cross-cultural communication strategy in the face of fierce competition and the rapid development of new media. Through the reflection and study of this case, students can master the theoretical knowledge of cultural archetype theory, cultural IP cross-border marketing strategy and cross-cultural communication strategy, and think about the cultural empowerment measures of domestic console games, so as to provide certain reference value for how other domestic console games can use traditional culture to create global popularity.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《品牌营销》、《文化营销》、《跨文化传播》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">USP营销策略；文化原型理论；文化认同感；跨文化传播策略；文化IP跨界营销；文化赋能</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
